{"tid":1214704,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野餐濕毛巾預防山火, 人人有責","createTime":"2019-06-13T05:04:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T05:38:08.000Z","uid":23249,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"aec906488d3e9426e2f717e06bd2c734722b1a58","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:04:18.000Z","msg":"鼓油：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1214271/page/2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1214271/page/2</a><br />\n#44 Kapok <br />\n<br />\n近日見大家對野餐興致勃勃，就想講下預防山火。大家都知道星星之火可以燎原，山火好多時都由一個小煙頭引起<br />\n<br />\n大家見到Ｄ撚樣恃住自己大隻就亂咁扔煙頭，咁大家文明人，打柒佢就唔岩既，我地要用愛與和平感化佢<br />\n<br />\n琴日大家好叻，識得用水淋熄煙頭，終於唔再驚二手煙，唔再即刻跑走驚生肺癌，但係淋水個效率我個人覺得比較低左Ｄ，驚Ｄ撚樣追住你黎打就唔好。<br />\n<br />\n呢排天氣咁熱，去野餐，有條濕毛巾或者一條乾毛巾加支水係好撚正常既事，大家一見到Ｄ撚樣再亂咁扔煙頭，即刻扔條濕毛巾過去，就唔會再有二手煙同咁易引起山火啦係咪？<br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有咩意見？<br />\n<br />\n預防山火，人人有責！"},{"pid":"fd72b42efd882fd8caf47bb001d01da40a4202cd","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:07:05.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"3ae3868932d22c2eb4387d7e54d3edcbedb491f3","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:07:48.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},{"pid":"cb010c70a49067d1d74078befa3141c1da2c599c","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ae3868932d22c2eb4387d7e54d3edcbedb491f3","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:07:48.000Z","msg":"ＰＵＳＨ"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:23:57.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"27997c5e06b41f7aa9c41e1ca609bc1959253a58","tid":1214704,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"唔好搞著消防員啦"},{"pid":"01408d4351a0551623edabba0e0ddb87e3292bc7","tid":1214704,"uid":104555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:26:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb0ed2dade7c132b56e29e5823a54d1e96b146b3","tid":1214704,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27997c5e06b41f7aa9c41e1ca609bc1959253a58","tid":1214704,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"唔好搞著消防員啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"係唔好搞大自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26801141b709b5888978fc75882737064f1275b5","tid":1214704,"uid":104086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:27:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a44f6bfb183206173aea265be4ff763d15db46c","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bb0ed2dade7c132b56e29e5823a54d1e96b146b3","tid":1214704,"uid":92385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27997c5e06b41f7aa9c41e1ca609bc1959253a58","tid":1214704,"uid":104555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:25:47.000Z","msg":"唔好搞著消防員啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:27:20.000Z","msg":"係唔好搞大自然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:28:33.000Z","msg":"維護乾淨環境，人人有責！"},{"pid":"44fbfd80b73b6bcd021689759f043059e1f293fa","tid":1214704,"uid":23249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T05:38:08.000Z","msg":"push"}]}